metadata.name: Frog Princess Fans Club
metadata.description: This is our flying "Frog Princess" Gu Ailing Eileen! She shined under the pressure, Her technique, dedication and sportsmanship are a joy. At the Beijing Winter Olympics, people cheered wildly for the new queen Gu Ailing on the big jumping platform! We Love the way she imagines herself jumping on top of a mountain. We treasure Gu Ailing Eileen's lovely and wonderful photos.
